clearFeedRoute.t.sol
├── when caller does not have the relevant role
│  └── it should revert with AccessManagedUnauthorized
└── when caller has the relevant role
   ├── given first price feed is null
   │  └── it should revert with PriceFeedRouteNotRegistered
   └── given first price feed is non null
      ├── it should clear the feed route for the provided token in oracle registry storage
      └── it should emit a FeedRouteCleared event
